      "writtenOn": "2018-02-23T16:30:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It allows clients to install temporary or special case crash signal handlers without tinkering with the real signal handler state which, assuming threads, is probably a risky operation.\n\nSpeaking concretely, V8 uses guard pages.\nhttps://cs.chromium.org/chromium/src/chrome/app/chrome_main_delegate.cc?rcl\u003dde7e59605f3184e374b3c5cf027eee4b85e7cab8\u0026l\u003d553",
